OL,3,CTrump says he'd speak to Hezbollah and
OL,4,Coffers 'a lot' of help to Lebanon
OL,6,FDonald Trump has pledged to help
OL,7,FLebanon "a lot" during a meeting with
OL,8,Fthe country's president, going as far
OL,9,Fas to suggest he would be willing to
OL,10,Fspeak to Hezbollah.
OL,12,FDuring the meeting at the White House
OL,13,Fwith Lebanese president Joseph Aoun on
OL,14,FTuesday, Trump said the country had
OL,15,Fbeen "very badly treated".
OL,17,FTrump noted on Tuesday Lebanon's
OL,18,F"Hezbollah problem" and suggested that
OL,19,Fhe personally could speak with the
OL,20,FIran-backed militant group if Aoun
OL,21,Fwanted him to.
OL,26,@zD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
