PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784751301
OL,3,CTrump says he'd speak to Hezbollah and
OL,4,Coffers 'a lot' of help to Lebanon
OL,6,FHe also floated the idea of having
OL,7,FSyria intervene to fight Hezbollah `
OL,8,Falthough the president didn't fully
OL,9,Fcommit to that.
OL,11,FSuch a concept would be highly
OL,12,Funpopular in Lebanon and potentially
OL,13,Fembarrass Aoun.
OL,15,FIsrael and Hezbollah, which is based
OL,16,Fin Lebanon, have been fighting an on-
OL,17,Foff war since the Hamas-led October 7
OL,18,Fattacks in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
