PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784751301
OL,3,CTrump says he'd speak to Hezbollah and
OL,4,Coffers 'a lot' of help to Lebanon
OL,6,FThe fighting intensified with the
OL,7,Foutbreak of the US-Israel war with
OL,8,FIran earlier this year.
OL,10,F"We're going to have it properly
OL,11,Ftreated and treated with the respect
OL,12,Fit deserves," Trump told Aoun during a
OL,13,Fmeeting which wrapped up the Lebanese
OL,14,Fleader's four-day visit to Washington.
OL,16,F"We're gonna help it a lot," he said,
OL,17,Fwithout giving concrete details.
OL,19,FAoun told Trump, "Your vision is
OL,20,Fpeace," calling it Trump's "legacy."
OL,26,@{D@ROU|D@GO]|D@\OU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
