PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784751301
OL,3,CTrump says he'd speak to Hezbollah and
OL,4,Coffers 'a lot' of help to Lebanon
OL,6,FThe US president responded by joking,
OL,7,F"I do agree with that" and said Aoun
OL,8,Fwas handsome and "knows how to get to
OL,9,Fme," adding: "Now he can have
OL,10,Fanything."
OL,12,FThe US has pushed for peace in Lebanon
OL,13,Fbut has been increasingly distracted
OL,14,Fby a new round of escalation with the
OL,15,Fwar in Iran, which has destabilised
OL,16,Fmuch of the Middle East.
OL,18,FOn Tuesday, Trump said he had little
OL,19,Finterest in talks with Iran's leader
OL,20,Fto end the war.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@ROUqD@DO]qD@NOUrD@JO]
