OL,3,CTrump says he'd speak to Hezbollah and
OL,4,Coffers 'a lot' of help to Lebanon
OL,6,FTrump told reporters that Iranian
OL,7,Fofficials "want to desperately meet",
OL,8,Fadding: "Until they're ready to meet
OL,9,Fin a meaningful way, we have no
OL,10,Finterest in meeting."
OL,12,FHe said the US would soon target the
OL,13,Farea near Pickaxe Mountain ` a
OL,14,Ffortified underground site near one of
OL,15,FIran's primary nuclear enrichment
OL,16,Ffacilities.
OL,18,FStrikes against Iran continued on
OL,19,FTuesday, despite the nominal peace
OL,20,Fdeal between Tehran and Washington.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@dO]pD@IOUrD@UO]
