OL,3,CTrump says he'd speak to Hezbollah and
OL,4,Coffers 'a lot' of help to Lebanon
OL,6,FIranian state media reported numerous
OL,7,Fsites across the country had been hit
OL,8,Fon Tuesday, and Iran retaliated with
OL,9,Fstrikes on Jordan and Bahrain.
OL,11,FThe UK's Maritime Trade Operations
OL,12,Fcentre said a tanker came under attack
OL,13,Fearly Tuesday in the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,14,Foff Oman, forcing the crew to abandon
OL,15,Fthe vessel.
OL,17,FIran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard
OL,18,FCorps (IRGC) claimed the attack, as
OL,19,Fwell as two other attacks on ships
OL,20,FMonday in the critical global shipping
OL,21,Froute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
