OL,3,CTrump says he'd speak to Hezbollah and
OL,4,Coffers 'a lot' of help to Lebanon
OL,6,FShipping through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,7,Fhas largely stalled, and as the fight
OL,8,Ffor control over the waterway
OL,9,Fintensifies, both sides have targeted
OL,10,Fcivilian infrastructure in the region
OL,11,Frelied on by millions of people.
OL,13,FA barrage of US strikes hasn't
OL,14,Fcompelled Tehran to loosen its grip on
OL,15,Fthe strait, through which about one-
OL,16,Ffifth of the world's crude oil and
OL,17,Fnatural gas was shipped before the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
