OL,3,CTrump says he'd speak to Hezbollah and
OL,4,Coffers 'a lot' of help to Lebanon
OL,6,FIn the Red Sea, Iran-backed Houthi
OL,7,Frebels have opened a new front against
OL,8,FSaudi Arabia by declaring a naval
OL,9,Fblockade of the kingdom, threatening
OL,10,Fthe flow of global oil supplies and
OL,11,Ftrade.
OL,13,FWith the Strait of Hormuz blocked up,
OL,14,FSaudi Arabia has been relying on a
OL,15,Fpipeline to the Red Sea to get
OL,16,Fmillions of barrels of oil out to
OL,17,Fmarket.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
